author: Frank Ocean
quote: Work hard in silence, let your success be your noise.

author: Bum Phillips
quote: The only discipline that lasts is self-discipline.

author: Thomas Jefferson
quote: If you want something you have never had, you must be willing to do something you have never done.

author: Neale Donald Walsch
quote: Life begins at the end of your comfort zone.

author: Zig Ziglar
quote: You don’t have to be great to start, but you have to start to be great.

author: James N. Watkins
quote: A river cuts through rock, not because of its power, but because of its persistence.

author: Ryan Blair
quote: If it is important to you, you will find a way. If not, you’ll find an excuse.

author: Tim Notke
quote: Hard work beats talent when talent doesn’t work hard.

author: Confucius
quote: It does not matter how slowly you go as long as you do not stop.

author: Karen Lamb
quote: A year from now you may wish you had started today.
